## Steps to Reproduce
With this chunk of code, an action is available to make an exhaustive switch case
```dart
enum Test {
  first,
  second;
  
  static const variable = 'const';
  
  String get getter {
    switch (this) {
      
    }
  }
}
```

When I used the action, I got this result
```dart
enum Test {
  first,
  second;

  static const variable = 'const';

  String get getter {
    switch (this) {

      case Test.first:
        // TODO: Handle this case.
        break;
      case Test.second:
        // TODO: Handle this case.
        break;
      case Test.variable:
        // TODO: Handle this case.
        break;
    }
  }
}
```
`case Test.variable` should not be added as it is not an enum value.

title: Autocomplete switch case in enum with static property does not work as expected
